messages.content: How do I install Davemane42's Custom Node for ComfyUI?
Navigate to the `/ComfyUI/custom_nodes/` folder, `git clone git clone https://github.com/Davemane42/ComfyUI_Dave_CustomNode`, and start ComfyUI.
What does the MultiAreaConditioning 2.4 node allow you to do?
The MultiAreaConditioning 2.4 node allows you to visualize the ConditioningSetArea node for better control and comes with a ConditioningUpscale node useful for high-resolution fix workflow.
What is the use of the ConditioningUpscale node?
The ConditioningUpscale node is useful for high-resolution fix workflow.
What is included in the MultiLatentComposite 1.1 node?
The MultiLatentComposite 1.1 node allows you to visualize the MultiLatentComposite node for better control.
What is one known issue with MultiLatentComposite 1.1?
One known issue with MultiLatentComposite 1.1 is that it does not check for out of bound layers.
